> Hide! Hide! Witch!  
> The good folk come to burn thee!  
> Their keen enjoyment hid beneath  
> The gothic mask of duty.

This are the opening lines in the story "Hide! Hide! Witch!" By Mark Clifton
And Alex Apostolides, in [Astounding Science Fiction, December
1953](http://www.luminist.org/archives/SF/AST/AST_1953_12_L.jpg).
